p: The current study is an effort carried out to understand the molecular interaction with bioactive volatiles from oils of Eucalyptus and Corymbia against SARS-CoV-2 specifically targeting M pro and to predict the pharmacokinetics and toxological parameters of the volatile compounds taken for study. The findings and studies of this investigation will be useful to the general public and will give researchers and scientists to bring out the correct medication to fight against COVID-19 by focusing on Mpro.
